CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FPictures from Leicestershire Police
OL,9,FThis was the moment an Uber driver who
OL,10,Fraped a passenger at knifepoint in
OL,11,FLeicester was caught by police just
OL,12,Fafter an hour later.
OL,14,FOfficers were able to find and arrest
OL,15,FAdam Daley shortly after the incident
OL,16,Fin December last year, after the woman
OL,17,Fhe attacked immediately contacted
OL,18,Fpolice.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHer rapid reporting of the offence
OL,8,Fenabled officers to carry out
OL,9,Fenquiries to identify the defendant's
OL,10,Fcar and track its movements through
OL,11,FCCTV and ANPR cameras.
OL,13,FCrucially, it also ensured vital
OL,14,Fforensic and digital evidence was
OL,15,Fpreserved.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FThis evidence proved key in securing
OL,8,FDaley's conviction and following a
OL,9,Ftrial last month he was found guilty
OL,10,Fof one count of rape, one count of
OL,11,Fsexual assault, one count of
OL,12,Fpossession of a bladed article and one
OL,13,Fcount of threats to kill.
OL,15,FCourage of the victim
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Majid Zaveri,
OL,8,Fsenior investigation officer, said:
OL,9,F"The courage of the victim and the
OL,10,Fprofessionalism and dedication of the
OL,11,Fresponse and investigation officers
OL,12,Fhas led to this outcome.
OL,14,F"My thanks go to the victim who
OL,15,Fbravery and co-operation led to this
OL,16,Fquick arrest and allowed vital
OL,17,Fevidence to be secured.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F"Thank you to the response officers
OL,8,Ffor their quick actions and to the
OL,9,Finvestigation team ` including
OL,10,FDetective Sergeants George White, Jon
OL,11,FDavies and Detective Constables Matt
OL,12,FSmith and Charlotte Worley ` for their
OL,13,Ftireless work to ensure the defendant
OL,14,Fwas brought before the courts.
OL,16,F"If you are a victim of a sexual
OL,17,Foffence, please know that we are here
OL,18,Fto listen to you, to help you and to
OL,19,Fsupport you. Please report to us or
OL,20,Fspeak with someone you can trust."
OL,26,@xD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FArresting Daley
OL,9,FThe rape was reported to police
OL,10,Fshortly after 5.30am on Monday,
OL,11,FDecember 29, and had taken place in
OL,12,Fthe back of Daley's white Toyota Auris
OL,13,Fin a layby close to Soar Valley Way.
OL,15,FThe victim, a woman in her 20s, and
OL,16,Fher friend had been outside a bar in
OL,17,FLeicester city centre about to order
OL,18,Fan Uber when Daley pulled up alongside
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe offered to take them both home if
OL,8,Fthey booked the trip through the app.
OL,9,FAfter dropping her friend home, Daley
OL,10,Fand the victim continued the journey
OL,11,Fto her address.
OL,13,FDuring the drive, Daley started making
OL,14,Fsexualised comments towards the victim
OL,15,Fand asking her inappropriate questions.
OL,17,FWhile heading out of the city, Daley
OL,18,Fthen pulled over in a layby ` claiming
OL,19,Fhe needed to go to the toilet.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe then ordered the victim to move
OL,8,Finto the front of the car, before
OL,9,Fforcing her to perform a sex act on
OL,10,Fhim by threatening her with a knife.
OL,12,FDuring this incident he also pulled
OL,13,Fdown the victim's top and touched her.
OL,15,FAfter pleading with Daley to stop, he
OL,16,Fleft the woman in the layby and sped
OL,17,Foff. She immediately called 999 and an
OL,18,Fofficer was dispatched to her.
OL,20,FDaley's capture
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FQuick enquiries identified the
OL,8,Fregistration of the vehicle and Daley
OL,9,Fas the insured driver.
OL,11,FOfficers on shift in the force's Roads
OL,12,FPolicing Team were put on alert and
OL,13,FDaley was stopped at the junction of
OL,14,FVaughan Way and Great Central Street
OL,15,Fat 6.37am.
OL,17,FWhile officers were attempting to
OL,18,Farrest Daley, he attempted to grab his
OL,19,Fphone and also to stamp on it - in a
OL,20,Fbid to destroy any evidence.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FWhile in custody, detectives began
OL,8,Fcarrying out extensive enquiries,
OL,9,Fincluding forensic examinations and
OL,10,Freviewing CCTV and mobile phone data
OL,11,Fin order to track the defendant's
OL,12,Fmovements both before and after the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,FDespite the victim's DNA being found
OL,16,Fon the defendant and his clothing,
OL,17,FDaley continued to deny the offence
OL,18,Fand claimed her DNA had transferred to
OL,19,Fhim as she had drunk from a water
OL,20,Fbottle in the car.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe claimed he had later used the same
OL,8,Fbottle to wash a part of his body
OL,9,Fafter urinating in the layby.
OL,11,FFollowing examination of his phone,
OL,12,Fdetectives were able to establish
OL,13,FDaley had driven past the victim while
OL,14,Fshe was in the layby three times after
OL,15,Fthe incident had taken place.
OL,17,F'Deeply traumatic and distressing
OL,18,Fexperience'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FDetective Constable Matt Smith from
OL,8,FSignal ` the force's rape and serious
OL,9,Fsexual assault team was the officer in
OL,10,Fthe case.
OL,12,FHe said: "I want to commend the victim
OL,13,Fin this case during what has been an
OL,14,Fextremely difficult six months.
OL,16,F"Her actions that night and the
OL,17,Fstrength and bravery she has shown
OL,18,Fduring the investigation and trial has
OL,19,Fensured a dangerous individual is now
OL,20,Fbehind bars.
OL,26,@tD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F"Despite her deeply traumatic and
OL,8,Fdistressing experience, that night she
OL,9,Fdemonstrated exceptional presence of
OL,10,Fmind and was able to contact police
OL,11,Fimmediately after Daley had driven off.
OL,13,F"Thanks to this, officers were able to
OL,14,Fact quickly to identify and locate the
OL,15,Fsuspect in a very short space of time.
OL,17,F"This was crucial to our investigation
OL,18,Fand ensured not only key forensic
OL,19,Fevidence could still be detected but
OL,20,Fthat he was apprehended before he
OL,21,Fattacked anyone else.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,F"Daley targeted a lone woman after she
OL,8,Ftrusted him to get her home safely.
OL,9,FGiven his job as an Uber driver it is
OL,10,Fpossible there could be more victims
OL,11,Fthat have not come forward.
OL,13,F"We take reports of sexual assault
OL,14,Fvery seriously and anyone who wishes
OL,15,Fto report offences will be spoken to
OL,16,Fby specialist officers in the team."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G14/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FSpecialist detectives from the force's
OL,8,Frape and serious sexual assault team,
OL,9,Fwho investigated the incident, are now
OL,10,Furging anyone else who could have been
OL,11,Fa victim of Daley's to come forward.
OL,13,FWhat was the sentence?
OL,15,FOn Friday (10 July), at Leicester
OL,16,FCrown Court, the 33-year-old of
OL,17,FChester Close, Leicester, was
OL,18,Fsentenced to a total of 16 years'
OL,19,Fimprisonment.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G15/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FHe has also been subject to a Sexual
OL,8,FHarm Prevention Order (SHPO) until
OL,9,Ffurther notice and a restraining order
OL,10,Fpreventing him from contacting the
OL,11,Fvictim.
OL,13,FAt sentencing, he also pleaded guilty
OL,14,Fto two counts of making incident
OL,15,Fimages of a child ` evidence found by
OL,16,Fofficers when his mobile phone was
OL,17,Fexamined.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G16/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FAt the time of his arrest, Daley also
OL,8,Frefused to provide a drugs wipe, so a
OL,9,Fblood sample was sent for testing and
OL,10,Flater came back as positive for
OL,11,Fcocaine.
OL,13,FHe was charged and pleaded guilty to
OL,14,Ftwo counts of drug driving at
OL,15,FLeicester Magistrates' Court on
OL,16,FWednesday 1 April.
OL,18,FHe was banned from driving for 20
OL,19,Fmonths, fined #200 and order to pay
OL,20,F#85 court costs and an #80 victim
OL,21,Fsurcharge.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G17/18
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
