FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784053122
OL,3,CUber driver who raped passenger at
OL,4,Cknifepoint caught by police an hour
OL,5,Clater
OL,7,FAn Uber spokesperson said: "This was a
OL,8,Ftruly shocking incident and something
OL,9,Fno one should ever go through. We have
OL,10,Fa dedicated Safety Support team who
OL,11,Fare available 24/7 to provide
OL,12,Fspecialist assistance following
OL,13,Fserious incidents and our team fully
OL,14,Fsupported the Police in their
OL,15,Finvestigation."
